            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-shopping-cart.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Expenses
            p.text-muted
              | Easily identify costs, split bills, and track balances between you and your roommates.
              | (Future support to graph expenses, settle debts directly through Venmo.)
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Calendar
            p.text-muted
              | View your roommates schedules, set reminders for bills and other deadlines, and never forget
